;The recombinant protein of HALT-1 was eluted with the estimated size of ~11kDa using HiLoad Superdex 75 PG 16/600 (GE Healthcare). The eluted protein was shown with size of ~22kDA in the SDS-PAGE suggests that, the protein is likely a monomer in the solution. It is not known why the protein was eluted with smaller size compared to the estimated size.
